Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多久才能登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會耽誤和土影使者的匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也盡快趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受夠了 感覺地面搖晃不止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來直到最後 凱的暈船症也沒能好轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡補給完物資後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往雷之國的路就不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些小意外 但還是順利完成任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌豚骨雖然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但海鮮的也不差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛停穩就飛奔了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正也要在這留宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且還是座小島 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在晃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之國離這座小島不遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是座小島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得太遠會給與我們接頭的人添麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦 我們來得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就抽空隨便看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復得真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 土影大人委派我做使者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自跟來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼見外嘛 赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之國一直未和我們建交
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒機會弄到情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然聯手了 但大家都是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見機行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是土影的使者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的小命…我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…我們是同盟國的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦 去死吧 巖隱村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖隱和霧隱怎麼在這裡打起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就打了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 木葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢阻撓的話 就算是木葉的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止我 長十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這麼做有違水影大人的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉命阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能做到的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點…可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼要襲擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是爭執的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉打雜的 你也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…打雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 這座島嶼非常偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大部隊裡有醫療忍者 他們正趕往這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾我拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別匯報了 快擦汗去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個遲鈍的雜役啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說誰是打雜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在這裡轉悠的 不就是些負責傳令的雜役嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話 快幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為啥要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才收到了水影大人的傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡有數名忍者突然間失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是反對這次忍者同盟的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心人物就是上忍巖流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷了赤土的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他是綠之峽悲劇事件的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠之峽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該知道 霧隱同巖隱長期交惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起事件就是其中一條導火線
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十多年前 曾收集各地忍術的雲隱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶過我們村裡的機密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我們和同盟巖隱一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由巖流帶隊 前去奪回文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心 雲隱的那幫傢伙就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 附近有巖隱的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個任務如果能成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以向諸國證明 巖隱和霧隱的同盟堅若磐石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 離和平又更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在期盼這一天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是盟友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務就是將文件帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能饒恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮 俊菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離和平又更近一步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直憎恨著巖隱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的結盟或許是他無法容忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到襲擊我們的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他想通過暗殺巖隱的使者來復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時破壞這個未曾抱有希望的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能被這些雜事干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被幹掉之前先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等…這件事是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我看好赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的世界正被仇恨所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我找不到答案的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將答案托付給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是唱哪出啊 打雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解 因為同伴被傷 你很憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我坐以待斃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果去了 雙方一定會有傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們互相殘殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說些莫名其妙的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能阻止就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不讓你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會放你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是個打雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會這麼麻煩的攔路之術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你快回你同伴那兒去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個使者離開了長十郎 正趕往這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊吧 巖流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我的父親被巖隱所殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替村活著的人多想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的憤怒和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切恩怨都由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是木葉的漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾人柱力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道大叔的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是來阻止大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的師父被佩因所殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能理解大叔的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還請罷手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你已經幹掉了佩因 報仇雪恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那傢伙只是氣數已盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你沒想過報仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對他的時候 我無法抑制恨意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身顫抖 恨不得立刻殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道 這樣是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為憎恨的輪迴就此開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦開始 復仇便會喚起復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的人們則不斷死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我早已心中有數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想實現她的願望只有一條路…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果此時引發復仇慘劇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五影們就會認真思考締結這個同盟的困難和危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 為了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各村不過是為各自的利益而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子間的同盟也會因各自的利益而輕鬆瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 忍者們為了村子的利益不斷背叛 對立 殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五大國之中 這個忍者世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有多少人在敵視別國忍者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是我 下次就會是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會像你一樣停止復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此膚淺的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會不斷重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會改變這樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何敢斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我繼承了師父和師兄的囑托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何消除仇恨的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何阻止復仇輪迴的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何讓忍者之間相互理解的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們二個信任我 我就一定要找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請大叔相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕進展緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡可能靠近和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離和平又更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 巖流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這緊要關頭摻和進來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 我可是全力砍下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不會死在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多事要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…死了可就是我的責任了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際糾紛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了 別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…好痛啊 只是休息了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不束手就擒的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 麻煩治好那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧忍的傢伙 赤土呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫療忍者到了我才過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說沒有性命之憂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖流先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是受被你所傷的使者所托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將綠之峽犧牲的忍者的遺物歸還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及就那次事件正式謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是土影大人派遣使者前來的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖隱…竟然會為那起事件謝罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個頑固的老頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了鞏固我們和霧隱的同盟關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大叔 會怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死罪就是流放吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟作出了這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也該有所覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為不小心摔倒才受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是為那起事件贖罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送霧隱一個人情嘛 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不僅僅是老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會連你也被風影感化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧影的傢伙 這只是給你們的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有木葉打雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有傷在身…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我的同伴還在等我 再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少報上姓名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這副慘狀是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢 不小心摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了…在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青葉 吐槽點不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 明天還要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好出發準備 早點休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 關於這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來消息說雷之國的船隻會直接來接我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一定就是引導我的章魚的說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙到底合不合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要說勉強也算合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爺我自古討厭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個愛說冷笑話的肌肉大叔是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陸 樂園之島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大叔 是八尾人柱力
